{"tid":1837124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「行動Post」 我地有一個月時間，準備全港大三罷！","createTime":"2020-01-23T13:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T09:45:51.000Z","uid":108757,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"516131c91c3785b81431bdca27b7e35b554e6df2","tid":1837124,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:06:27.000Z","msg":"事到如今，唔需要再叫政府封關乜柒柒喇，要封一早封咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<span style=\"color: red;\">用多啲時間諗下點樣令「肺炎」事件幫助抗爭好過。</span>共產黨宜家已經去到懸崖邊，我地要做嘅就係伸多佢一腳。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n農曆新年完咗之後，大約係二月初，香港將會有大量病毒感染，而<span style=\"color: red;\">病毒潛伏期大約14日，即係二月中至二月尾，香港就會進入第一波社區大爆發</span>，每日會出現數十宗至過百宗個案，之後就真係自求多福。換言之，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地仲有大約一個月時間做文宣，為應對社區大爆發嘅大三罷去宣傳。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而呢次三罷，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔需要黎明行動或者塞鐵</span>，完全自發，返工撚要返工由得佢返，佢好快就會病到唔洗返。手足只要留喺屋企，做好物資準備就夠。所有學生罷課，非緊急職業進入無限期罷工，緊急職業可以選擇照罷工，或維持有限度服務，或者按章工作，直至疫病消失為止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解要三罷？</span><br />\n1. 手足要<span style=\"color: red;\">明哲保身</span><br />\n留喺屋企可以盡量降低染病機會，等藍屍出去食病毒，我地自保就夠。<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">搶佔先機</span>同道德高地<br />\n我地要<span style=\"color: red;\">早過政府出聲</span>，向市民呼籲疫病社區爆發嘅危機。如果我地一早呼籲罷工，而大家知道<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭係中計撚，政府一定會鬥氣死都唔肯宣布停工停課</span>，而導致疫病惡化。如此我地就做英雄，政府就做殺人兇手。<br />\n<br />\n3. 直接造成龐大經濟損失，<span style=\"color: red;\">加劇攬炒</span>情況<br />\n<br />\n4. 儲夠人數<br />\n工會可以開始向會員派發問卷，<span style=\"color: red;\">統計一下會員對罷工嘅意向</span>，再有一個月嘅時間俾我地儲氣，到時一次過爆，威力一定好大。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">宜家應該做咩？</span><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">準備文宣</span>，宣傳未來大三罷。用「保命」作為焦點，「不分黃藍，保命要緊」。現時可以呼籲「減少出行」、「減少消費」、「儲蓄資金應急」等等，開始對經濟進行攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n2. 工會開始<span style=\"color: red;\">做罷工意向投票統計</span>，睇下會員傾向去到咩程度先開始罷工，例如「第一宗死亡個案」、「第一百宗確診個案」、「一日之內多於五十宗確診個案」等等，再同所有工會討論，<span style=\"color: red;\">發出三罷聯合聲明</span>。<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">儲蓄糧食、物資、金錢</span>，作長期罷工之用。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好以為以上所有野係吹水，好快就會變成真實！<br />\n仲望？做野喇！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb0224c23343927e11e5d7c7556b2d63173f960","tid":1837124,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:07:33.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 武漢肺炎天賜比香港人打爆港共嘅機會，做嘢啦！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1835841\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1835841</a><br />\n<br />\n參考PO"},{"pid":"8e3d867859cbc487edc1555360054e6cd9b451cb","tid":1837124,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb65918546eced46c6d99ff96bd4791c0b1db43","tid":1837124,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26b9abbba51a84f2a31f970060d5bcb1606ce5e","tid":1837124,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:10:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［行動］高鐵送肺炎，所以香港人會自救<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f2ed3b2b210ecbe725427458842af3976a8b8a24","tid":1837124,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:12:06.000Z","msg":"action post push first, ask questions later"},{"pid":"abf1ce9be4d4ad97efcef36f0bb6570f6b61fe4e","tid":1837124,"uid":108757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:12:29.000Z","msg":"點解唔即刻罷？<br />\n因為要儲氣，一鋪收佢皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec398493b2a3835c71a71f6765e738996429ac2d","tid":1837124,"uid":33304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:12:31.000Z","msg":"順便自我隔離"},{"pid":"fecc6555e270b9105a8dec794abb3f9aac86fa0b","tid":1837124,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2211d348827e3d19107d55ece0ef62ba1efff631","tid":1837124,"uid":6741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:15:42.000Z","msg":"「行動亅「「「開定」」今晚23:59...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837009</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fd82524e119ea91cd09cb75a3ef39f28bcdb6f60","tid":1837124,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486986ddf4b75aeac377855a952a3359b9cb70e6","tid":1837124,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:17:30.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n但個前題係個病毒真係會大爆發"},{"pid":"7b0541b64589df7f4070d183293f52e6d5d63528","tid":1837124,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"486986ddf4b75aeac377855a952a3359b9cb70e6","tid":1837124,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:17:30.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n但個前題係個病毒真係會大爆發"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:18:56.000Z","msg":"唔洗擔心，已經過萬病源體嚟咗香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520f45292c3afef9e8605cec596c5ab7ac9b5d2e","tid":1837124,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de103e314e8fbd59635d0598d2ccde1405558b95","tid":1837124,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite